# Local-only secret template for `wrangler dev`. COPY to `.dev.vars` (which is
# gitignored) and paste a real key there for LOCAL testing only. Never commit a
# real key. For production, use `wrangler secret put OPENAI_API_KEY` instead —
# the value is stored encrypted in Cloudflare, never in the repo.
OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-REPLACE_ME_LOCAL_ONLY"
